{"tid":2382452,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"跨性別演員Elliot Page 宣布與妻子離婚 結束3年婚姻","createTime":"2021-01-27T09:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T09:42:14.000Z","uid":318316,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aa69254457e481e64db73d9015c34399bd96fd6b","tid":2382452,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"憑參演電影《Juno少女孕記》（Juno）、《潛行凶間》（Inception）而為人熟悉的Ellen Page，早年公開出櫃後，再於上月宣布成為跨性別人士，改名為Elliot Page。當時Elliot獲太太Emma Portner全力支持，不過今日就有外國傳媒爆出，兩人昨日在紐約法院申請離婚，結束3年婚姻。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/579805/elliot-page%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E8%AE%8A%E6%80%A7%E5%BE%8C%E9%A9%9A%E7%88%86%E5%90%8C%E8%88%9E%E8%B9%88%E5%93%A1%E5%A6%BB%E5%AD%90%E9%9B%A2%E5%A9%9A-%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E4%BB%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F579805%2Felliot-page%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2580%25A7%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%25A9%259A%25E7%2588%2586%25E5%2590%258C%25E8%2588%259E%25E8%25B9%2588%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25A6%25BB%25E5%25AD%2590%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%25A9%259A-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591%25E4%25BB%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%259C%258B%25E5%258F%258B&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn0cGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=df8739a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/579805/elliot-page%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E8%AE%8A%E6%80%A7%E5%BE%8C%E9%A9%9A%E7%88%86%E5%90%8C%E8%88%9E%E8%B9%88%E5%93%A1%E5%A6%BB%E5%AD%90%E9%9B%A2%E5%A9%9A-%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E4%BB%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B</a>"}]}